{
  "number": 5188,
  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/5188",
  "title": "Proposal: Improve accessibility",
  "body": "> Discussion on: https://paper.dropbox.com/doc/InstantSearch-accessibility--AIdRtTIt19VrHIG4OABe31KPAg-RaDyCmcTvKpi8JShVD5sY\r\n\r\nAccessibility is an important topic and we should be responsible for it as we generate the DOM for our users. Accessibility is UX. We should raise awareness, include this concept in our workflow and respect standards.\r\n\r\nI went through all widgets and took notes of accessibility improvements we need to address in the next InstantSearch versions implementing InstantSearch.css. I added sources to back up the proposed changes.\r\n\r\nLet's discuss about them - feel free to add more suggestions. If you agree with this new markup, I will create a PR.\r\n\r\n## Breadcrumb\r\n\r\n- Use `nav` with `aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\"`\r\n- Use ordered list (`ol`)\r\n- Add `aria-current=\"page\"` to active element\r\n\r\n### Template\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"ais-Breadcrumb\">\r\n  <ol class=\"ais-Breadcrumb-list\">\r\n    <li class=\"ais-Breadcrumb-item\">\r\n      <a class=\"ais-Breadcrumb-link\" href=\"#\">Home</a>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class=\"ais-Breadcrumb-item\">\r\n      <span class=\"ais-Breadcrumb-separator\" aria-hidden=\"true\">></span>\r\n      <a class=\"ais-Breadcrumb-link\" href=\"#\" aria-current=\"page\">Cooking</a>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class=\"ais-Breadcrumb-item ais-Breadcrumb-item--selected\">\r\n      <span class=\"ais-Breadcrumb-separator\" aria-hidden=\"true\">></span>\r\n      Kitchen textiles\r\n    </li>\r\n  </ol>\r\n</nav>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Sources\r\n\r\n- https://www.w3.org/TR/wai-aria-practices/examples/breadcrumb/index.html\r\n- http://a11y-style-guide.com/style-guide/section-navigation.html#kssref-navigation-pagination\r\n\r\n## CurrentRefinements\r\n\r\n- Use new list for category refinements\r\n\r\n### Template\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<div class=\"ais-CurrentRefinements\">\r\n  <ul class=\"ais-CurrentRefinements-list\">\r\n    <li class=\"ais-CurrentRefinements-item\">\r\n      <span class=\"ais-CurrentRefinements-label\">\r\n        Category:\r\n      </span>\r\n      <ul>\r\n        <li class=\"ais-CurrentRefinements-category\">\r\n          <span class=\"ais-CurrentRefinements-categoryLabel\">Movies & TV Shows</span>\r\n          <button class=\"ais-CurrentRefinements-delete\">✕</button>\r\n        </li>\r\n        <li class=\"ais-CurrentRefinements-category\">\r\n          <span class=\"ais-CurrentRefinements-categoryLabel\">Others</span>\r\n          <button class=\"ais-CurrentRefinements-delete\">✕</button>\r\n        </li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n    </li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <button class=\"ais-CurrentRefinements-reset\">\r\n    Clear all\r\n  </button>\r\n</div>\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Highlight\r\n\r\n- Use `mark`\r\n\r\n### Template\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<span class=\"ais-Highlight\"><span class=\"ais-Highlight-nonHighlighted\">This is the</span> <mark class=\"ais-Highlight-highlighted\">highlighted text</mark></span>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Sources\r\n\r\n- https://www.w3schools.com/tags/tag_mark.asp\r\n\r\n## Pagination\r\n\r\n- Use `nav`\r\n- Add `aria-label=\"Pagination\"`\r\n- Use ordered list (`ol`)\r\n- Add `aria-current=\"page\"` to active element\r\n\r\n### Template\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<nav aria-label=\"Pagination\" class=\"ais-Pagination\">\r\n  <ol class=\"ais-Pagination-list\">\r\n    <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--firstPage ais-Pagination-item--disabled\">\r\n      <span class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" aria-label=\"Previous\">‹‹</span>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--previousPage ais-Pagination-item--disabled\">\r\n      <span class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" aria-label=\"Previous\">‹</span>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--selected\">\r\n      <a class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"#\" aria-current=\"page\">1</a>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--page\">\r\n      <a class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"#\">2</a>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--page\">\r\n      <a class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"#\">3</a>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item\">\r\n      <a class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"#\">4</a>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--nextPage\">\r\n      <a class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" aria-label=\"Next\" href=\"#\">›</a>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--lastPage\">\r\n      <a class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" aria-label=\"Next\" href=\"#\">››</a>\r\n    </li>\r\n  </ol>\r\n</nav>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Sources\r\n\r\n- http://a11y-style-guide.com/style-guide/section-navigation.html#kssref-navigation-pagination\r\n- https://tink.uk/using-the-aria-current-attribute/\r\n\r\n## Panel\r\n\r\n- Use `header` for the header\r\n- Use `footer` for the footer\r\n\r\n### Template\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<div class=\"ais-Panel\">\r\n  <header class=\"ais-Panel-header\">Header</header>\r\n  <div class=\"ais-Panel-body\">Panel content</div>\r\n  <footer class=\"ais-Panel-footer\">Footer</footer>\r\n</div>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Sources\r\n\r\n- https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\r\n- https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\r\n\r\n## RefinementList\r\n\r\n- Use ordered list (`ol`) because it can be searchable\r\n\r\n### Template\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<div class=\"ais-RefinementList\">\r\n  <div class=\"ais-RefinementList-searchBox\">\r\n    <!-- SearchBox widget here -->\r\n  </div>\r\n  <ol class=\"ais-RefinementList-list\">\r\n    <li class=\"ais-RefinementList-item ais-RefinementList-item--selected\">\r\n      <label class=\"ais-RefinementList-label\">\r\n        <input class=\"ais-RefinementList-checkbox\" type=\"checkbox\" value=\"Insignia™\" checked=\"\" />\r\n        <span class=\"ais-RefinementList-labelText\">Insignia™</span>\r\n        <span class=\"ais-RefinementList-count\">746</span>\r\n      </label>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class=\"ais-RefinementList-item\">\r\n      <label class=\"ais-RefinementList-label\">\r\n        <input class=\"ais-RefinementList-checkbox\" type=\"checkbox\" value=\"Samsung\">\r\n        <span class=\"ais-RefinementList-labelText\">Samsung</span>\r\n        <span class=\"ais-RefinementList-count\">633</span>\r\n      </label>\r\n    </li>\r\n  </ol>\r\n  <button class=\"ais-RefinementList-showMore\">Show more</button>\r\n</div>\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Snippet\r\n\r\n- Use `mark`\r\n\r\n### Template\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<span class=\"ais-Snippet\"><span class=\"ais-Snippet-nonHighlighted\">This is the</span> <mark class=\"ais-Snippet-highlighted\">snippet text</mark></span>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Sources\r\n\r\n- https://www.w3schools.com/tags/tag_mark.asp",
